title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-30-2013 MON
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-30-2013 MON.............PODCAST




The Glenn Beck Program


Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
The Glenn Beck Program - 12/30/13Monday, December 30, 2013 11:33 AM





Chris Salcedo is in for Glenn today and he's calling for Eric Holder's resignation,

 pointing out that the Attorney General picks and chooses
     when he decides to uphold the law, 
       making race a decision factor. 

 Also, Iraq has fallen into civil war after American troops have withdrawn,

     Chris thinks Afghanistan about to follow suit as US and Nato troops lay out an exit strategy.


  Plus, Texas Congressman Steve Stockman joins the program to discuss
           his attempt to take the TX senate seat of John Cornyn.
